description: Internal alterations comprising: relocation of plant room from levels 4 & 5 to 3 & 4, change of use of 5th floor (north tower, plant room) and 3rd (south tower, medical centre) to residential use to create 15 additional residential apartments, revise use at 2nd floor from use class D1 (medical centre only) to use classes B1, D1, D2 & A3, revise use at 1st floor from use class A1 (retail only) to use classes A1 & A3.
